summary:
Just some presets I made while bored,hope you like them :)

Comes with two presets,Jess The Warrior and Galaxy Jess The Warrior :)
descriptionHtml:
Mod comes with two presets,Galaxy Jess The Warrior,a colorful alien version of Jess,and Jess the Warrior,just the human Jess that's cute with some warpaint :)

Mods to use with this:
-Any hair mod,doesn't matter which one you use.
-Graphene Block 20 or 30 (off Tumblr,can't link cuz NSFW but with a quick Google search you can find the skin :)
-The Eyes Of Beauty or The Eyes Of Aber
-facelight(recommended,gives the face some light in the darkness for screenshots and for your character to look good in the dark)
-Dimonized UNP Body or UUNP(need this for the skin mod i mentioned on here)

Well,that's it,enjoy the mod! :)
